  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim is to study the specific lung elastance in ALI/ARDS patients during
      invasive mechanical ventilation, in supine and prone position.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In sedated and paralyzed ALI/ARDS patients, we study and compare the specific lung elastance
      in supine and prone position during invasive mechanical ventilation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
